 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'enkafan', 'comment_id': 244792615.0, 'datetime': '2016-09-05 17:52:37+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_2', 'text': 'Slightly related, I was working on calling my build script from VS Code. Maybe this new section could also house this information too. For what it's worth, here's the config I settled on.

```json
